snippet: Fred Couples, 52, shot the lowest score of the day, a five-under 67, to move into the lead with Jason Dufner after two rounds at the Masters.
abstract: Fred Couples and Jason Dufner share second-round lead at the Masters golf tournament.
lead_paragraph: Fred Couples, 52, shot the lowest score of the day, a five-under 67, to move into the lead with Jason Dufner after two rounds at the Masters.

headline.seo: Couples, 52, Earns Share of Masters Lead
headline.main: Tied for Lead, Couples Feels Young Again at Augusta
